, "name": "iphone", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_normal.png?m=1630643991", "title": "iPhone", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone", "topics": 12957, "footer": "这里绝不讨论如何获得 iPhone 盗版软件、iTunes 黑卡之类。", "header": "Say hello to the future.", "title_alternative": "iPhone", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991", "stars": 3617, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 8, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"id": 653928, "username": "16cfecc", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/16cfecc", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ac307b155c916449381eb6963240589e?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ac307b155c916449381eb6963240589e?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ac307b155c916449381eb6963240589e?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1696842956, "last_modified": 1780036727, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Rorysky", "last_touched": 1780099840, "title": "使用 iPhone 的同学，是如何解决门禁卡方案的呢？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216457", "created": 1780036728, "deleted": 0, "content": "总是忘记带门禁卡，希望大家多分享下自己的最佳实践。", "content_rendered": "<p>总是忘记带门禁卡，希望大家多分享下自己的最佳实践。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780036728, "replies": 57, "id": 1216457}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 71294, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9694, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 793169, "username": "liandro", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/liandro", "website": "https://imagetovideoai.net", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "独立开发", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ab4/ce65/793169_mini.png?m=1776828776", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ab4/ce65/793169_normal.png?m=1776828776", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ab4/ce65/793169_large.png?m=1776828776", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ab4/ce65/793169_xlarge.png?m=1776828776", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ab4/ce65/793169_xxlarge.png?m=1776828776", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ab4/ce65/793169_xxxlarge.png?m=1776828776", "created": 1773205837, "last_modified": 1776828776, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Rorysky", "last_touched": 1780118446, "title": "AI 把我调教了，从 0 消费，到月消费 1200 元。", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216578", "created": 1780065455, "deleted": 0, "content": "AI 把我调教了。\r\n\r\n一路走下来的订阅路程：\r\n\r\n- 最早用国产 Kimi\r\n- 订阅 minimax 2.5 （¥25 还是 ¥35 不记得了）\r\n- 用 opencode （内部跑的也是 minimax ）\r\n- 阿里百炼的订阅（¥20 、¥30 一个业务）\r\n- 咸鱼上买 antigravity 家庭组（¥157/月）+ codex pro （当时 ¥20/月）\r\n- 全面转 codex 20 倍，2 人拼车，相当于 10 倍（¥650/月）\r\n- 加上 claude Pro （¥85 左右一个人）\r\n- 现在：codex 20 倍拼车（¥650/月） + claude Pro 5 倍（¥575/月）\r\n\r\n从今年 3 月中到现在 5 月底，2 个半月，我已经被调教到没有 AI 活不了的地步了。\r\n\r\n看了下统计，近一个月用了 76 亿的 token 。\r\n\r\nAI 的费用越来越高，依赖也越来越高。不知道是好是坏。", "content_rendered": "<p>AI 把我调教了。</p>\n<p>一路走下来的订阅路程：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>最早用国产 Kimi</li>\n<li>订阅 minimax 2.5 （¥25 还是 ¥35 不记得了）</li>\n<li>用 opencode （内部跑的也是 minimax ）</li>\n<li>阿里百炼的订阅（¥20 、¥30 一个业务）</li>\n<li>咸鱼上买 antigravity 家庭组（¥157/月）+ codex pro （当时 ¥20/月）</li>\n<li>全面转 codex 20 倍，2 人拼车，相当于 10 倍（¥650/月）</li>\n<li>加上 claude Pro （¥85 左右一个人）</li>\n<li>现在：codex 20 倍拼车（¥650/月） + claude Pro 5 倍（¥575/月）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>从今年 3 月中到现在 5 月底，2 个半月，我已经被调教到没有 AI 活不了的地步了。</p>\n<p>看了下统计，近一个月用了 76 亿的 token 。</p>\n<p>AI 的费用越来越高，依赖也越来越高。不知道是好是坏。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780065455, "replies": 41, "id": 1216578}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_large.png?m=1630576706", "name": "invest", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_normal.png?m=1630576706", "title": "投资", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/invest", "topics": 3562, "footer": "", "header": "Can you make money with money?", "title_alternative": "Invest", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_mini.png?m=1630576706", "stars": 4446, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 171, "parent_node_name": "money"}, "member": {"id": 485116, "username": "pddgoods", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/pddgoods", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15c3/7ea8/485116_mini.png?m=1754448027", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15c3/7ea8/485116_normal.png?m=1754448027", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15c3/7ea8/485116_large.png?m=1754448027", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15c3/7ea8/485116_xlarge.png?m=1754448027", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15c3/7ea8/485116_xxlarge.png?m=1754448027", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15c3/7ea8/485116_xxxlarge.png?m=1754448027", "created": 1587432178, "last_modified": 1754448027, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "zli", "last_touched": 1780056834, "title": "我们大 A 又又又发生了什么？需要我们股民买单？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216450", "created": 1780035942, "deleted": 0, "content": "外围天天恐慌性上涨，我们天天慢牛中股灾", "content_rendered": "<p>外围天天恐慌性上涨，我们天天慢牛中股灾</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780035942, "replies": 34, "id": 1216450}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 10939, "footer": "", "header": "生